metadata.name: Princess of the Moon
metadata.description:
Princess of the Moon
The princess of the moon, named Tara, lived in a city called the moon, a very beautiful city with a pleasant climate . . . The people there are very good and hospitable people.
Tara, Princess of the Moon, is a very smart and kind girl. Tara's mother (Sasha) is the Queen of the City of Moon A very powerful and political queen. The big problem is that the Queen of the City has a dictatorial and strict government.
Tara has a lot of fans among the people, everyone loves Tara because Tara listens to the voice of the people and did her best for freedom and helping the people.
But it was not easy to confront the queen. Those who adhered to the queen to maintain the government enjoyed great benefits, so they were even willing to sacrifice their lives to protect the queen and maintain the rule.
Tara decided to leave the city to learn more and find people who could help her along the way . . .
The story continues . . .
